{{Infobox medical condition | Name = Twin anemia-polycythemia sequence | Image = File:TAPS_legs_twins.jpg | Caption = Twin anemia-polycythemia sequence is a monochorionic twin condition characterized by a large intertwin hemoglobin difference }}
'''Twin anemia-polycythemia sequence''', abbreviated as '''TAPS''', is a form of chronic inter-twin transfusion.<ref name="elsevier47">{{Cite journal|title = Twin Anemia–Polycythemia Sequence in Two Monochorionic Twin Pairs Without Oligo-Polyhydramnios Sequence|url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0143400406000154|journal = Placenta|pages = 47–51|volume = 28|issue = 1|doi = 10.1016/j.placenta.2006.01.010|pmid = 16516289|first = E.|last = Lopriore|first2 = J.M.|last2 = Middeldorp|first3 = D.|last3 = Oepkes|first4 = H.H.|last4 = Kanhai|first5 = F.J.|last5 = Walther|first6 = F.P.H.A.|last6 = Vandenbussche|year = 2007}}</ref><ref name="wkhealth753">{{Cite journal|title = Placental Characteristics in Monochorionic Twins With and Without Twin Anemia–Polycythemia Sequence|url = http://content.wkhealth.com/linkback/openurl?sid=WKPTLP:landingpage&an=00006250-200810000-00005|journal = Obstetrics & Gynecology|pages = 753–758|volume = 112|issue = 4|doi = 10.1097/aog.0b013e318187e1ff|first = E|last = Lopriore|first2 = J|last2 = Deprest|first3 = F|last3 = Slaghekke|first4 = D|last4 = Oepkes|first5 = J M.|last5 = Middeldorp|first6 = F P. H. A.|last6 = Vandenbussche|first7 = L|last7 = Lewi|year = 2008}}</ref><ref name="elsevier514">{{Cite journal|title = The outcome of monochorionic diamniotic twin gestations in the era of invasive fetal therapy: a prospective cohort study|url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0002937808003451|journal = American Journal of Obstetrics and Gynecology|pages = 514.e1–514.e8|volume = 199|issue = 5|doi = 10.1016/j.ajog.2008.03.050|first = Liesbeth|last = Lewi|first2 = Jacques|last2 = Jani|first3 = Isaac|last3 = Blickstein|first4 = Agnes|last4 = Huber|first5 = Leonardo|last5 = Gucciardo|first6 = Tim Van|last6 = Mieghem|first7 = Elisa|last7 = Doné|first8 = Anne-Sophie|last8 = Boes|first9 = Kurt|last9 = Hecher|year = 2008|pmid=18533114}}</ref><ref name="karger181">{{Cite journal|title = Twin Anemia-Polycythemia Sequence: Diagnosti